    <h1 class="policy-h1">DMCA Policy</h1>
    
    <p>DealsHub India values the rights of creators and expects its users to do the same. To comply with the Digital Millennium Copyright Act of 1998, we will promptly address claims of copyright infringement involving the DealsHub India Blog service.</p>
    
    <h2 class="policy-h2">Reporting Copyright Infringement</h2>
    <p>To report alleged copyright infringement, please provide a Notice containing:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Identification of the copyrighted work claimed to have been infringed.</li>
      <li>The URL of the link shown on the website where such material may be found.</li>
      <li>Your contact information (mailing address, telephone number, and email).</li>
      <li>A statement of good faith belief that the use is not authorized by the copyright owner.</li>
      <li>A statement that the information in the Notice is accurate, under penalty of perjury.</li>
    </ul>
    
    <div class="policy-contact-block">
      <div class="policy-contact-label">Designated Copyright Agent</div>
      <a href="mailto:squeamish27@gmail.com" class="policy-contact-email">squeamish27@gmail.com</a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="policy-footer-nav">
      <a href="/" class="policy-back-link">&larr; Back to Home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</PolicyLayout>
